 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> sollte nicht aufgerufen werden, bevor das Dokument, das es implementiert, das Laden abgeschlossen hat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-157">Sie können erkennen, wann das Laden eines Dokuments abgeschlossen ist, indem Sie das- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> Ereignis behandeln.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-157">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-158">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie eine Skriptfunktion in einem Dokument aus einer- [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] Anwendung mithilfe von aufgerufen wird <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-158">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-159">In diesem Beispiel weist die Skriptfunktion keine Parameter auf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-159">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-160">Im folgenden finden Sie das [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] Dokument, das die Skriptfunktion implementiert, die von aufgerufen wird [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-160">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-161">Das folgende Beispiel zeigt die- [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] Implementierung, um die Skriptfunktion im Dokument aufzurufen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-161">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> sollte nicht aufgerufen werden, bevor das Dokument, das es implementiert, das Laden abgeschlossen hat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-170">Sie können erkennen, wann das Laden eines Dokuments abgeschlossen ist, indem Sie das- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> Ereignis behandeln.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-170">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-171">Wenn Sie nicht genügend Parameterwerte an das Skript übergeben, das Sie aufrufen, haben die Parameter, an die Sie keine Werte übergeben, den undefinierten Wert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-171">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-172">Wenn Sie zu viele Parameterwerte übergeben, werden die überzähligen Werte ignoriert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-172">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-173">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Skriptfunktionen in einem-Dokument aus einer-Anwendung mithilfe von aufgerufen werden <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-173">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-174">In diesem Beispiel erfordern die Skriptfunktionen Parameter.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-174">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-175">Im folgenden finden Sie das Dokument, das die Skriptfunktionen implementiert, die von aufgerufen werden [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-175">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-176">Das folgende Beispiel zeigt die- [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] Implementierung zum aufzurufen der Skriptfunktionen im [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] Dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-176">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-190">Der Aufruf von <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> hat denselben Effekt wie das Festlegen der- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> Eigenschaft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-190">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> wird von Entwicklern verwendet, die deklarativ das ursprüngliche Dokument angeben möchten, zu dem <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigiert, wenn <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> initialisiert wird.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-192">Verwenden Sie die- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> Methode, um zu einer URL zu navigieren, die Escapezeichen enthalten kann.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-192">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-193">Verwenden Sie die- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> Methode, um zu einer zu navigieren <xref:System.Uri> , die keine Escapezeichen enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-193">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-194">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> mithilfe der-Methode zu einem Dokument navigiert werden kann <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-194">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-212">Verwenden Sie die- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> Methode, um zu einer URL zu navigieren, die Escapezeichen enthalten kann.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-212">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-213">Verwenden Sie die- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> Methode, um zu einer zu navigieren <xref:System.Uri> , die keine Escapezeichen enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-213">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-214">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Sie zu einem Dokument navigieren und es in einem neuen Browserfenster öffnen, indem Sie das Ziel "about: blank" angeben.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-214">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-225">Wenn der- `stream` Parameter ist `null` , wird <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> zu einem leeren Dokument ("about: blank") navigiert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-225">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-226">Wenn der Stream-Parameter nicht in einem gültigen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] Format vorliegt, wird er als nur-Text angezeigt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-226">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-227">Nach der Navigation ist <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> `null` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-227">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7cd9a-228">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Sie zu einem Stream navigieren können, der ein Dokument enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cd9a-228">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
